    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-threshold factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted on the basis that the regulatory submission scope is explicitly limited to static compression-bending performance under ASTM F1717, and no dynamic or fatigue claims are made. Overall model credibility is sufficient to support the Medium model risk level and Medium decision consequence. Package accepted with documented acknowledgment of the test conditions gap.",
